examples.en: We received an order to attack.
She had a sudden heart attack.
examples.ru: У неё внезапно случился сердечный приступ.

examples.en: She had an attack of hiccups.
Acid attacks metals.
The attack began at dawn.
Our troops attacked the enemy.
His plan of attack was misguided
The enemy attacked treacherously.
He suffered a major heart attack.
He made a blistering attack on his opponent.
examples.ru: Он яростно набросился на своего оппонента.

examples.en: He suffered a mild heart attack.
An attack of fever carried him off.
examples.ru: Приступ лихорадки свёл его в могилу.

examples.en: They live in constant dread of another attack.
examples.ru: Они живут в постоянном страхе, еще одной атаки.

examples.en: Rust is attacking the metal.
There is a threat of nuclear attack.
Stress can bring on an asthma attack.
They were at the head of the attack.
examples.ru: Они были во главе этой атаки. / Они возглавили нападение.

examples.en: The government has come under attack.
Attacks on women increased last year.
examples.ru: В прошлом году число нападений на женщин увеличилось.

examples.en: The troops attacked at dawn.
They launched a deadly attack.
The troops repulsed the attack.
He suffered a minor heart attack.
The base was braced for an attack.
The attack refuelled fears of war.
He had a heart attack and croaked.
examples.ru: У него случился сердечный приступ, и он окочурился.

examples.en: The visiting team started to attack.
Troops attacked the fortress at dawn.
He was the victim of a savage attack.
They made a new attack on the problem.
examples.ru: Они вновь энергично приступили к решению этой проблемы.
